## üÜï What's New

### v1.3.0 (2025-10-21)

**New Features:**
- ‚ú® **Mermaid theme support** - Choose from 5 color themes: `default`, `neutral`, `dark`, `forest`, `base`
- ‚ú® **Mermaid quality control** - Scale factor 1-4 for diagram resolution (CLI: `--mermaid-scale`, API: `mermaid_scale`)
- ‚ú® **Automatic emoji removal** - Emoji characters are removed for PDF compatibility (clean text output)
- ‚ú® **Hyperlink handling** - Markdown hyperlinks `[text](url)` are converted to plain text for readability

**Bug Fixes:**
- üêõ **Fixed Mermaid diagram sizing** - Canvas-based rendering ensures exact dimensions, no whitespace issues
- üêõ **Fixed diagram quality** - High-resolution rendering (2x scale by default) for crisp, professional diagrams
- üêõ **Improved spacing** - Better margins around Mermaid diagrams (0.3cm before, 0.5cm after)
- üêõ **Fixed hyperlink rendering** - Links no longer cause rendering issues in table of contents

**Breaking Changes:**
- üìù Emoji are now automatically removed from text (previously rendered as ÔøΩ or boxes)
- üìù Hyperlinks are now converted to plain text (full clickable support planned for future version)

---

### v1.2.0 (2025-10-20)

- ‚ú® **Full Unicode/UTF-8 support** - Multilingual text, special characters (‚Ä¢, √®, √†, etc.)
- ‚ú® **Customizable fonts** - Choose Arial, DejaVu, Helvetica, or provide custom TTF file
- ‚ú® **Bold & inline code in lists** - Full markdown formatting support in bullet/numbered lists
- ‚ú® **Larger Mermaid diagrams** - Use full page width for better readability
- üêõ **Fixed encoding issues** - Bullet characters and accented text now display correctly
- üîß **Automatic font detection** - Auto-selects best Unicode font for your system
